fields.title: Mixer
fields.description:
Attaches to Power Hub Of your stand mixer and uses the power of the motor to run the attachment
Fits all Household KitchenAid Stand Mixers
With 6 quick-change blades and an optional peeling blade to inspire healthy versions of classic recipes and unleash your culinary potential
3 Spiraling Blades - Medium, Fine, and Extra Fine; 3 Slicing Blades - Slicing (Large Core), Slicing (Small Core), and Thin Slice (Small Core); Peeling Blade
All Blades are dishwasher safe on the top rack. The body can be wiped clean with a warm damp cloth

fields.title: Camera
fields.description:
Slim body size with transparent ring lens
Automatic Exposure - The Mini 11 automatically selects the optimal shutter speed in any environment. Mini 11 captures bright backgrounds and bright subjects, even in dark scenes.
1-touch Selfie Mode – the Mini 11 has a built-in macro mode and a selfie mirror for the perfect selfie. You don’t need a close-up lens attachment. Just pull out the lens barrel until the “Selfie Mode” mark appears
Customize your camera - 2 shutter button accessories are included - Jewel button and a glow button.
2 - AA batteries

fields.title: Sweat pants
fields.description:
50% Cotton, 50% Polyester
Imported
Machine Wash
50 percent cotton/50 percent polyester fleece, with up to 5 percent made from recycled plastic bottles

fields.title: Cars
fields.description: Lightning McQueen is living in the fast lane - until he hits a detour and gets stranded in Radiator Springs; a forgotten town on Route 66. There he meets a heap of hilarious characters who help him discover there's more to life than fame.
